# Laravel Inertia.js Page Generator

**Command**: `/laravel:inertia-page [name] [options]`

**Description**: Generates complete Inertia.js pages with Laravel backend, Vue.js/React frontend, form handling, and comprehensive testing.

## Usage

```bash
/laravel:inertia-page UserProfile --with-form
/laravel:inertia-page ProductCatalog --with-search --with-filters --framework=vue
/laravel:inertia-page Dashboard --with-charts --framework=react
/laravel:inertia-page BlogPost --crud --with-editor --slug-based
```

## Options

- `--framework=vue|react` - Choose frontend framework (auto-detected if not specified)
- `--with-form` - Include form handling with validation
- `--with-search` - Add search functionality
- `--with-filters` - Include filtering capabilities
- `--with-pagination` - Add pagination support
- `--with-charts` - Include chart.js integration
- `--with-editor` - Add rich text editor (TinyMCE/Quill)
- `--crud` - Generate complete CRUD operations
- `--slug-based` - Use slug-based routing
- `--real-time` - Enable real-time features
- `--with-auth` - Include authentication guards
- `--modal` - Create as modal page
- `--nested` - Create nested page structure

## Generated Files

### Backend Files
- `app/Http/Controllers/{Name}Controller.php` - Inertia controller
- `app/Http/Requests/{Name}Request.php` - Form validation (if --with-form)
- `app/Http/Resources/{Name}Resource.php` - API resource for data transformation
- `routes/web.php` - Updated with new routes

### Frontend Files (Vue.js)
- `resources/js/pages/{name}/index.vue` - Main page component
- `resources/js/pages/{name}/create.vue` - Create form (if --crud)
- `resources/js/pages/{name}/show.vue` - Detail view (if --crud)
- `resources/js/pages/{name}/edit.vue` - Edit form (if --crud)
- `resources/js/components/{name}/` - Reusable components
- `resources/js/composables/use-{name}.js` - Vue composables for logic

### Frontend Files (React)
- `resources/js/pages/{name}/index.jsx` - Main page component
- `resources/js/pages/{name}/create.jsx` - Create form (if --crud)
- `resources/js/pages/{name}/show.jsx` - Detail view (if --crud)
- `resources/js/pages/{name}/edit.jsx` - Edit form (if --crud)
- `resources/js/components/{name}/` - Reusable components
- `resources/js/hooks/use-{name}.js` - Custom React hooks

### Testing Files
- `tests/Feature/{Name}ControllerTest.php` - Backend tests
- `resources/js/Tests/{Name}.test.js` - Frontend tests (Jest/Vitest)

## Implementation Examples

### Laravel Controller (Inertia Backend)
```php
<?php

namespace App\Http\Controllers;

use App\Http\Requests\ProductRequest;
use App\Http\Resources\ProductResource;
use App\Models\Product;
use App\Models\Category;
use Illuminate\Http\Request;
use Inertia\Inertia;

class ProductController extends Controller
{
    public function index(Request $request)
    {
        $products = Product::query()
            ->with(['category', 'images'])
            ->when($request->search, function ($query, $search) {
                $query->where('name', 'like', "%{$search}%")
                      ->orWhere('description', 'like', "%{$search}%");
            })
            ->when($request->category, function ($query, $category) {
                $query->where('category_id', $category);
            })
            ->when($request->price_range, function ($query, $range) {
                [$min, $max] = explode(',', $range);
                $query->whereBetween('price', [$min, $max]);
            })
            ->orderBy($request->sort_by ?? 'created_at', $request->sort_order ?? 'desc')
            ->paginate(15)
            ->withQueryString();

        return Inertia::render('Products/Index', [
            'products' => ProductResource::collection($products),
            'categories' => Category::select('id', 'name')->get(),
            'filters' => $request->only(['search', 'category', 'price_range']),
            'sort' => $request->only(['sort_by', 'sort_order']),
        ]);
    }

    public function create()
    {
        return Inertia::render('Products/Create', [
            'categories' => Category::select('id', 'name')->get(),
        ]);
    }

    public function store(ProductRequest $request)
    {
        $product = Product::create($request->validated());

        if ($request->hasFile('images')) {
            foreach ($request->file('images') as $image) {
                $product->images()->create([
                    'path' => $image->store('products', 'public'),
                    'alt_text' => $request->input('alt_text', $product->name)
                ]);
            }
        }

        return redirect()->route('products.index')
            ->with('success', 'Product created successfully.');
    }

    public function show(Product $product)
    {
        $product->load(['category', 'images', 'reviews.user']);

        return Inertia::render('Products/Show', [
            'product' => new ProductResource($product),
            'related_products' => ProductResource::collection(
                Product::where('category_id', $product->category_id)
                    ->where('id', '!=', $product->id)
                    ->limit(4)
                    ->get()
            ),
        ]);
    }

    public function edit(Product $product)
    {
        return Inertia::render('Products/Edit', [
            'product' => new ProductResource($product),
            'categories' => Category::select('id', 'name')->get(),
        ]);
    }

    public function update(ProductRequest $request, Product $product)
    {
        $product->update($request->validated());

        return redirect()->route('products.show', $product)
            ->with('success', 'Product updated successfully.');
    }

    public function destroy(Product $product)
    {
        $product->delete();

        return redirect()->route('products.index')
            ->with('success', 'Product deleted successfully.');
    }
}
